        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">According to OECD, EDTA is mainly produced and used as acid (H4EDTA). In the European Union, the production is 53900 tonnes of EDTA as H4EDTA equivalents.

Reference(s):
OECD. 2004. Screening Information Dataset, Initial Assessment profile for SIAM 18. Retrieved from: http://webnet.oecd.org/hpv/ui/handler.axd?id=84727fdb-7fba-4892-8da0-7a1781186edf, 15 June 2017.</productionVolumeComment>
